docs.lead_paragraph: The appointment of Dempster McIntosh as United States Ambassador to Colombia has been rushed through the Senate Foreign Relations Committee and the Senate without discussion. This is surprising, considering the recent controversies over political appointees.

docs.lead_paragraph: A civil engineer, 28-year-old Gilson Macedo-Soares, is making history in the South American dog world. He is the youngest president in the history of the Brazil Dog Club. And his miniature pinscher, Lady Lety de Guararema, has won more honors than any other dog in Brazil.
